
Agenda :

- Routing and navigation
* Router Module
* Dynamic routing
- Pipes
* Built in pipes 
* Custom pipes
- Services
- Dependency Injection 

Routing :

- navigate between pages and display appropriate component on the browser

full match : /home
prefix : /home/1

wildcard : **

Pipes :(|)

- Transform your data into specific format

Structure :

input data ---> | ------>Transformed data

1.Built in pipes

- Lower case and upper case
- Number pipe
- currency pipe
- date pipe
- percent pipe

eg:
jeni --->|(touppercase)----> JENI

18 ----> | ---> $18

2/2/2024 12:59:00:00 ---> | ----> 2024/2/2

2. Custom Pipe 

eg :
jeni--->(|)----> Miss.Jeni


